        in the morning, and all the folk-people began to come to him, and he sat teaching them. 3The Scribes
        and the Pharisees brought him a woman caught by surprise in adultery, and stood her right in front of
        everyone. 4They said to him, “Teacher, this here woman was caught in the very act of adultery. 5Now in
