        <char style="it">brace yourself </char>in Mark 10:49. This same remark used to be used in English but
        has dropped out of usage. In <char style="it">Snow White and the Seven Dwarfs, </char>Doc tells the other
        dwarfs, <char style="it">Courage, men, courage!, </char>before they scrub themselves with soap and water.</char>
