  <chapter number="17" style="c" sid="JHN 17" />
    <para style="p">
      <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JHN 17:1" />Jesus said these things then lifted his eyes up to the sky, to where heaven is, and said, <char style="wj">“Father,
        my time has arrived. Glorify Your son this once, so that the son would glorify You, </char><verse eid="JHN 17:1" />
      <verse number="2" style="v" sid="JHN 17:2" /><char style="wj">just as You’ve given him authority over every imaginable being</char><char style="sup">[a]</char><char
        style="wj">, so that he would give that special fullness of life, eternal life, to all those who’ve been
        given to him. </char><verse eid="JHN 17:2" />
      <verse number="3" style="v" sid="JHN 17:3" /><char style="wj">Eternal life is this: that they would know and understand You, the Only True God and
        Jesus Christ the Messiah whom You sent. </char><verse eid="JHN 17:3" />
      <verse number="4" style="v" sid="JHN 17:4" /><char style="wj">I have glorified You upon the earth, having completed the works You’ve given me to do.
        </char><verse eid="JHN 17:4" />
      <verse number="5" style="v" sid="JHN 17:5" /><char style="wj">At this juncture in time, glorify me this once, Father, using your inherent glory, the
        glory which came from you, the glory which you ever had before the world came into being.</char><verse eid="JHN 17:5" />
    </para>
    <para style="p">
      <verse number="6" style="v" sid="JHN 17:6" /><char style="wj">”I’ve made Your reputation and everything you stand for</char><char style="sup">[b]</char><char
        style="wj"> manifest to the people You’ve given to me from among those in the world. They were with You,
        and You gave them to me, and they have kept Your system of thought</char><char style="sup">[c]</char><char
        style="wj">. </char><verse eid="JHN 17:6" />
      <verse number="7" style="v" sid="JHN 17:7" /><char style="wj">By now they’ve come to understand that everything You’ve given me is from You; </char><verse eid="JHN 17:7" />
      <verse number="8" style="v" sid="JHN 17:8" /><char style="wj">that the sayings which You gave me, I’ve given to them. They whole-heartedly took it
        all in</char><char style="sup">[d]</char><char style="wj"> and have come to know and understand the truth
        that went forth from You, and have believed that You sent me. </char><verse eid="JHN 17:8" />
      <verse number="9" style="v" sid="JHN 17:9" /><char style="wj">I ask </char><char style="it"><char style="wj">in matters </char></char><char style="wj">concerning
        them; I don’t ask </char><char style="it"><char style="wj">in matters </char></char><char style="wj">concerning
        the world, the established order of humans, but rather concerning those whom You’ve given me, because
        they are with You. </char><verse eid="JHN 17:9" />
      <verse number="10" style="v" sid="JHN 17:10" /><char style="wj">All that is mine is Yours, and Yours mine, and I have been glorified in them. </char><verse eid="JHN 17:10" />
      <verse number="11" style="v" sid="JHN 17:11" /><char style="wj">No longer am I </char><char style="it"><char style="wj">to stay </char></char><char
        style="wj">in the world (but they are in the world), but I’m heading Your way. Holy Father, hold them
        fast this once, they whom You’ve given me, in everything You stand for</char><char style="sup">[b]</char><char
        style="wj">, so that they would be in unity</char><char style="sup">[e]</char><char style="wj"> the same
        way we </char><char style="it"><char style="wj">are. </char></char><verse eid="JHN 17:11" />
      <verse number="12" style="v" sid="JHN 17:12" /><char style="wj">When I was with them, I never ceased to hold they whom You’ve given me fast in everything
        that You stand for</char><char style="sup">[b]</char><char style="wj">, and I was on the lookout and
        guarded </char><char style="it"><char style="wj">them</char></char><char style="wj">, and not a single
        one of them perished except the one who had self-destruction written all over him</char><char style="sup">[f]</char><char
        style="wj">, so that the Scriptures be fulfilled.</char><verse eid="JHN 17:12" />
    </para>
    <para style="p">
      <verse number="13" style="v" sid="JHN 17:13" /><char style="wj">”But at this time I’m heading Your way, and </char><char style="it"><char style="wj">while
        still </char></char><char style="wj">in the world I speak these things so that they might have My Fulfilled
        Joy within them. </char><verse eid="JHN 17:13" />
      <verse number="14" style="v" sid="JHN 17:14" /><char style="wj">I have given them Your system of thought</char><char style="sup">[c]</char><char style="wj">,
        and the world (the established order of humans) hated them, because they are not part of</char><char
        style="sup">[g]</char><char style="wj"> the world in the same way that I am not part of the world. </char><verse eid="JHN 17:14" />
      <verse number="15" style="v" sid="JHN 17:15" /><char style="wj">I’m not asking that You remove them from the world, but that You keep them from the
        Evil One</char><char style="sup">[h]</char><char style="wj"> instead</char><char style="it"><char style="wj">.
        </char></char><verse eid="JHN 17:15" />
      <verse number="16" style="v" sid="JHN 17:16" /><char style="wj">They are not a part of</char><char style="sup">[g]</char><char style="wj"> the world
        in the same way that I am not part of the world. </char><verse eid="JHN 17:16" />
      <verse number="17" style="v" sid="JHN 17:17" /><char style="wj">Partition them off this once, separating them in the truth: Your system of thought</char><char
        style="sup">[c]</char><char style="wj"> is truth. </char><verse eid="JHN 17:17" />
      <verse number="18" style="v" sid="JHN 17:18" /><char style="wj">In the same way that you sent me into the world, I too sent them into the world. </char><verse eid="JHN 17:18" />
      <verse number="19" style="v" sid="JHN 17:19" /><char style="wj">And on their behalf, I separate myself and keep myself holy, in order that they too
        would be partitioned and separated in truth.</char><verse eid="JHN 17:19" />
    </para>
    <para style="p">
      <verse number="20" style="v" sid="JHN 17:20" /><char style="wj">”I don’t ask this request only, but </char><char style="it"><char style="wj">I</char></char><char
        style="wj"> also </char><char style="it"><char style="wj">ask </char></char><char style="wj">concerning
        those who believe in me by way of their discourse, </char><verse eid="JHN 17:20" />
      <verse number="21" style="v" sid="JHN 17:21" /><char style="wj">so that everyone would be in unity</char><char style="sup">[e]</char><char style="wj">,
        just as You, Father, are united with me, and I am united with You; so that they would be united in us,
        in order that the world would believe that You sent me. </char><verse eid="JHN 17:21" />
      <verse number="22" style="v" sid="JHN 17:22" /><char style="wj">And I have given to them the glory which You have given me, so that they would be unified
        in the same way we are unified, </char><verse eid="JHN 17:22" />
      <verse number="23" style="v" sid="JHN 17:23" /><char style="wj">I in them and You in me, so that they would be made complete in unity, so that the world
        would know and understand that You sent me and that You loved them in the same way that You loved me.
        </char><verse eid="JHN 17:23" />
      <verse number="24" style="v" sid="JHN 17:24" /><char style="wj">Father, those whom You’ve given me—I want those people to be at the same place I’m at
        too, in order for them to behold My Glory, the glory which You’ve given to me because You loved me before
        time even began</char><char style="sup">[i]</char><char style="wj">.</char><verse eid="JHN 17:24" />
    </para>
    <para style="p">
      <verse number="25" style="v" sid="JHN 17:25" /><char style="wj">”Righteous Father, to add to this: the world doesn’t know or understand You, but I know
        and understand You. They haven’t known and understood that You sent me. </char><verse eid="JHN 17:25" />
      <verse number="26" style="v" sid="JHN 17:26" /><char style="wj">I have made known to them Your reputation and everything you stand for</char><char style="sup">[b]</char><char
        style="wj">, and I am </char><char style="it"><char style="wj">still in the process of </char></char><char
        style="wj">making </char><char style="it"><char style="wj">everything You stand for </char></char><char
        style="wj">known </char><char style="it"><char style="wj">to them</char></char><char style="wj">, so
        that the love which You loved me with would be in them, and that I would be in them.”</char><verse eid="JHN 17:26" />
    </para>
